{"id":16,"parent_id":1,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":16,"title":"Genesis 15","subtitle":"","short_title":"Gen.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 15"],[".studySummary",["i","Abram desires offspring—The Lord promises him seed in number as the stars—Abram believes the promise—His seed will be strangers in Egypt—Then, after four generations, they will inherit Canaan."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.1","order":"02.02.015.1353"},["b","1"],"After these things the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto Abram in a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"vision"],", saying,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Fear not"],", Abram: I",["i","am"],"thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"shield"],",",["i","and"],"thy exceeding great reward."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.2","order":"02.02.015.1354"},["b","2"],"And Abram said, Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", what wilt thou give me, seeing I go childless, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"steward"],"of my house",["i","is"],"this Eliezer of Damascus?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.3","order":"02.02.015.1355"},["b","3"],"And Abram said, Behold, to me thou hast given no seed: and, lo,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"one"],"born in my house is mine heir."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.4","order":"02.02.015.1356"},["b","4"],"And, behold, the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","came"],"unto him, saying, This shall not be thine heir; but he that shall come forth out of thine own bowels shall be thine heir."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.5","order":"02.02.015.1357"},["b","5"],"And he brought him forth abroad, and said, Look now toward heaven, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"tell"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"stars"],", if thou be able to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"number"],"them: and he said unto him, So shall thy",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_5d"},"seed"],"be."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.6","order":"02.02.015.1358"},["b","6"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"And"],"he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"believed"],"in the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; and he counted it to him for",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.7","order":"02.02.015.1359"},["b","7"],"And he said unto him, I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that brought thee out of Ur of the Chaldees, to give thee this land to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"inherit"],"it."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.8","order":"02.02.015.1360"},["b","8"],"And he said, Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", whereby shall I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"know"],"that I shall inherit it?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.9","order":"02.02.015.1361"},["b","9"],"And he said unto him, Take me an heifer of three years old, and a she goat of three years old, and a ram of three years old, and a turtledove, and a young pigeon."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.10","order":"02.02.015.1362"},["b","10"],"And he took unto him all these, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"divided"],"them in the midst, and laid each piece one against another: but the birds divided he not."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.11","order":"02.02.015.1363"},["b","11"],"And when the fowls came down upon the carcases, Abram drove them away."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.12","order":"02.02.015.1364"},["b","12"],"And when the sun was going down, a deep sleep fell upon Abram; and, lo, an horror of great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"darkness"],"fell upon him."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.13","order":"02.02.015.1365"},["b","13"],"And he said unto Abram, Know of a surety that thy seed shall be a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"stranger"],"in a land",["i","that is"],"not theirs, and shall serve them; and they shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"afflict"],"them four hundred years;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.14","order":"02.02.015.1366"},["b","14"],"And also that nation, whom they shall serve, will I judge: and afterward shall they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"come"],"out with great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"substance"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.15","order":"02.02.015.1367"},["b","15"],"And thou shalt go to thy fathers in peace; thou shalt be buried in a good",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"old"],"age."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.16","order":"02.02.015.1368"},["b","16"],"But in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"fourth"],"generation they shall come",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"hither"],"again: for the iniquity of the Amorites",["i","is"],"not yet",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"full"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.17","order":"02.02.015.1369"},["b","17"],"And it came to pass, that, when the sun went down, and it was dark, behold a smoking furnace, and a burning lamp that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"passed"],"between those pieces."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.18","order":"02.02.015.1370"},["b","18"],"In the same day the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"made a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"covenant"],"with Abram, saying, Unto thy seed have I given this",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"land"],", from",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"the river of Egypt"],"unto the great river, the river",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"Euphrates"],":"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.19","order":"02.02.015.1371"},["b","19"],"The Kenites, and the Kenizzites, and the Kadmonites,"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.20","order":"02.02.015.1372"},["b","20"],"And the Hittites, and the Perizzites, and the Rephaims,"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.21","order":"02.02.015.1373"},["b","21"],"And the Amorites, and the Canaanites, and the Girgashites, and the Jebusites."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.1a","order":"02.02.015.1374"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vision"},"TG Vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.1b","order":"02.02.015.1376"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/26.24"},"Gen. 26:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.17"},"1 Ne. 22:17"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/courage"},"TG Courage"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fearful"},"Fearful"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.1c","order":"02.02.015.1378"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/protection-divine"},"TG Protection, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.2a","order":"02.02.015.1380"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/24.2"},"Gen. 24:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.3a","order":"02.02.015.1382"},["b","3a"],["span.small","HEB"],"a son of my house.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/14.14"},"Gen. 14:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.5a","order":"02.02.015.1384"},["b","5a"],["span.small","HEB"],"count."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.5b","order":"02.02.015.1386"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/10.22"},"Deut. 10:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/9.23"},"Neh. 9:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.30"},"D&C 132:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.5c","order":"02.02.015.1388"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/27.23"},"1 Chr. 27:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"5d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.5d","order":"02.02.015.1390"},["b","5d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seed-of-abraham"},"TG Seed of Abraham"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.6a","order":"02.02.015.1392"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-gen/15.9-12"},["span.small","JST"],"Gen. 15:9–12 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.6b","order":"02.02.015.1394"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.6c","order":"02.02.015.1396"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.7a","order":"02.02.015.1398"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/32.18"},"Num. 32:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.8a","order":"02.02.015.1400"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/6.17.17-18"},"Judg. 6:17 (17–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/20.8.8-9"},"2 Kgs. 20:8 (8–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.18.18-19"},"Luke 1:18 (18–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.10a","order":"02.02.015.1402"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/34.18.18-19"},"Jer. 34:18 (18–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.12a","order":"02.02.015.1404"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.15.15-17"},"JS—H 1:15 (15–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.13a","order":"02.02.015.1406"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-bondage-of-in-egypt"},"TG Israel, Bondage of, in Egypt"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stranger"},"Stranger"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.13b","order":"02.02.015.1408"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/1.11.10-11"},"Ex. 1:11 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.25.23-25"},"1 Ne. 17:25 (23–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.14a","order":"02.02.015.141